ditions%20remain%20stable%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20may%20not%20fall%20as%20much.%20But%20if%20the%20labor%20market%20weakens%20and%20the%20Fed%20has%20to%20cut%20rates%20more%20aggressively%2C%20we%20could%20see%20rates%20drop%20substantially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERates%20are%20unlikely%20to%20drop%20back%20down%20to%20the%20historic%20lows%20of%202020%20and%202021%2C%20when%2030-year%20fixed%20rates%20fell%20below%203%25.%20But%20we%20could%20see%20them%20settle%20in%20the%205%25%20range%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Will%20Home%20Prices%20Drop%20in%202024%3F%5C%22%3EWill%20Home%20Prices%20Drop%20in%202024%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20aren't%20likely%20to%20see%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fhome-prices-drop%5C%22%3Ehome%20prices%20drop%3C%2Fa%3E%20anytime%20soon%20thanks%20to%20extremely%20limited%20supply.%20In%20fact%2C%20they'll%20likely%20rise%20this%20year%20as%20mortgage%20rates%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fanniemae.com%2Fmedia%2F53421%2Fdisplay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFannie%20Mae%20researchers%3C%2Fa%3E%20expect%20prices%20to%20increase%205.8%25%20in%202024%2C%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mba.org%2Fnews-and-research%2Fforecasts-and-commentary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMortgage%20Bankers%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20expects%20a%203.8%25%20increase%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELower%20mortgage%20rates%20will%20bring%20more%20buyers%20onto%20the%20market%2C%20putting%20upward%20pressure%20on%20prices.%20But%20prices%20aren't%20expected%20to%20increase%20as%20much%20as%20they%20have%20in%20recent%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20to%20Choose%20a%20Mortgage%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20Choose%20a%20Mortgage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20options%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20the%20right%20%3Ca