r%20borrowers%20who%20want%20stability%2C%20since%20your%20monthly%20principal%20and%20interest%20payments%20won't%20change%20throughout%20the%20life%20of%20the%20loan%20(though%20your%20mortgage%20payment%20could%20increase%20if%20your%20taxes%20or%20insurance%20go%20up).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20exchange%20for%20this%20stability%2C%20you%20may%20get%20a%20higher%20rate.%20This%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20bad%20deal%20right%20now%2C%20but%20if%20rates%20increase%20further%20down%20the%20road%2C%20you%20might%20be%20glad%20to%20have%20a%20rate%20locked%20in.%20And%20if%20rates%20trend%20down%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20refinance%20to%20snag%20a%20lower%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EConventional%20vs.%20Government-Backed%20Mortgages%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fconventional-mortgage%5C%22%3EConventional%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20home%20loans%20that%20aren't%20backed%20by%20a%20government%20agency.%20They're%20often%20a%20good%20option%20for%20borrowers%20with%20strong%20credit%20scores.%20Conventional%20loans%20allow%20down%20payments%20as%20low%20as%203%25%2C%20though%20putting%20at%20least%2020%25%20down%20will%20allow%20you%20to%20avoid%20paying%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fpmi-private-mortgage-insurance%5C%22%3Eprivate%20mortgage%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20types%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fgovernment-home-loans%5C%22%3Egovernment-backed%20mortgages%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Ffha-loan%5C%22%3EFHA%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Allow%20credit%20scores%20down%20to%20580%20and%203.5%25%20down%20payments%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fva-loans%5C%