0ended.%20Recalling%20a%20lighthearted%20moment%20with%20his%20registrar%20judicial%20the%20previous%20evening%2C%20he%20shared%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20registrar%20judicial%20asked%20me%20what%20time%20the%20ceremonial%20should%20begin%2C%20I%20said%202%20pm%2C%20thinking%20it%20would%20allow%20us%20to%20wrap%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20pending%20items.%20But%20I%20wondered%20to%20myself-will%20anyone%20actually%20be%20here%20at%202%20pm%20on%20a%20Friday%20afternoon%3F%20Or%20will%20I%20just%20be%20left%20looking%20at%20myself%20on%20the%20screen%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20his%20career%2C%20he%20described%20the%20role%20of%20judges%20as%20akin%20to%20pilgrims%2C%20coming%20to%20court%20each%20day%20with%20a%20commitment%20to%20serve.%20%26quot%3BThe%20work%20we%20do%20can%20make%20or%20break%20cases%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20paid%20tribute%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bgreat%20judges%20who%20have%20adorned%20this%20court%20and%20passed%20on%20the%20baton%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20he%20felt%20reassured%20leaving%20the%20bench%20in%20the%20capable%20hands%20of%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20whom%20he%20praised%20as%20an%20able%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20have%20ever%20hurt%20anyone%20in%20the%20court%2C%20please%20forgive%20me%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20quoting%20the%20Jain%20phrase%20%26quot%3BMichhami%20Dukkadam%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20translates%20to%20%26quot%3BMay%20all%20my%20misdeeds%20be%20forgiven.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawyers%20and%20members%20of%20the%20bar%20gathered%20to%20honour%20the%20outgoing%20Chief%20Justice%2C%20describing%20him%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20rock%20star%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%2C%20who%20has%20been%20nominated%20as%20his%20successor%20and%20will%20be%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%2051st%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20on%20November%2011%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20never%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20appear%20in%20Justice%20Chandrachud's%20court%2C%20but%20what%20he%20has%20done%20for%20the%20marginalised%20and%20the%20needy%20is%20beyond%20compare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20a%20personal%20anecdote%20about%20Justice%20Chandrachud's%20fondness%20for%20samosas%2C%20remarking%20that%20they%20were%20served%20in%20nearly%20every%20meeting%2C%20though%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20himself%20refrained%20from%20eating%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud's%20tenure%20saw%20many%20changes%20within%20the%20court%2C%20from%20the%20establishment%20of%20Mitti%20Cafe%2C%20a%20facility%20empowering%20individuals%20with%20disabilities%2C%20to%20a%20dedicated%20bar%20room%20for%20women%20lawyers%2C%20alongside%20other%20beautification%20projects%20for%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20two-year%20term%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20authored%20a%20series%20of%20landmark%20judgments.%20Notably%2C%20he%20presided%20over%20the%20Constitution%20Bench%20upholding%20the%20revocation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20which%20redefined%20the%20politics%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20ordering%20that%20elections%20be%20conducted%20by%20September%202024%20and%20stressing%20the%20need%20to%20restore%20statehood%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20earliest%20and%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20significant%20judgement%2C%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20declined%20to%20alter%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%20to%20recognise%20same-sex%20marriages%2C%20deferring%20to%20the%20legislature.%20However%2C%20he%20insisted%20on%20the%20right%20of%20the%20LGBTQ%2B%20community%20to%20be%20treated%20with%20dignity%2C%20free%20from%20discrimination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20also%20led%20the%20decision%20to%20dismantle%20the%20controversial%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20mandating%20greater%20transparency%20in%20political%20financing%20and%20ordering%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20to%20cease%20issuing%20elect