your%20service%2C%20asking%20for%20investment)%2C%20save%20it%20for%20after%20your%20conversation%20unless%20it%20comes%20up%20naturally%20or%20if%20it%20was%20the%20intention%20of%20your%20original%20conversation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F12-questions-every-founder-should-ask-investors-micah-rosenbloom-vc-2020-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAdding%20in%20an%20ask%3C%2Fa%3E%20sneakily%20might%20throw%20them%20off%20and%20derail%20the%20conversation.%20They%20might%20think%20you're%20just%20%3Cem%3Eschmoozing%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeel%20free%20to%20ask%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20can%20I%20help%3F%26quot%3B%20but%20only%20if%20you%20mean%20it.%20This%20gives%20you%20an%20opportunity%20to%20be%20helpful%20and%20follow%20up%20with%20something%20valuable.%20In%20building%20relationships%2C%20I%20follow%20the%20rule%20of%3A%20Give%2C%20Give%2C%20Give%2C%20Ask.%20Give%20thrice%20before%20you%20ask%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b260126c-98ce-425a-ba6b-304c3004906c%5C%22%3E6.%20Bring%20a%20gift%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fgifts%2Fgifts-for-boss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGift-giving%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20when%20done%20right%2C%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20way%20to%20build%20new%20relationships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20mean%20bringing%20flowers%20(yikes)%20or%20buying%20them%20a%20new%20Rolex%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20metaphorical%20gift%20that%20has%20business%20value.%20Research%20the%20person%20you%20want%20to%20meet%20and%20bring%20them%20new%20ideas%20to%20solve%20their%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20had%20coffee%20with%20an%20exited%20entrepreneur%20who%20sold%20his%20company%20for%20nine%20figures%20and%20was%20building%20a%20new%20startup%20in%20a%20different%20space%20I%20was%20familiar%20with.%20I%20prepared%20five%20ideas%20that%20I%20believed%20could%20improve%20his%20branding%20and%20product%20strategy%2