r%20it's%20another%20country%20or%20whether%20it's%20a%20terrorist%20organization%2C%20our%20industry%20has%20been%20vigilant%20for%20quite%20some%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referencing%20two%20fires%20at%20DHL%20warehouses%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20have%20been%20linked%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20to%20cause%20fear%20and%20panic%2C%20but%20we%2C%20as%20a%20community%2C%20are%20not%20going%20to%20let%20them.%20One%20of%20our%20overriding%20messages%20is%20that%20we're%20vigilant%2C%26quot%3B%20Fried%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20officials%20have%20said%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspy-chief-warns-suspected-sabotage-nearly-caused-plane-crash-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efires%2C%20which%20took%20place%20at%20two%20DHL%20sites%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20Germany%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%2C%20may%20have%20been%20part%20of%20Russian%20sabotage%20operations%20that%20ultimately%20aimed%20to%20target%20North%20America%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Fworld%2Frussia-plot-us-planes-incendiary-devices-de3b8c0a%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20earlier%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20package%20caught%20fire%20before%20being%20loaded%20onto%20a%20plane%20at%20a%20DHL%20freight%20center%20in%20Leipzig%2C%20eastern%20Germany%2C%20while%20a%20similar%20incident%20took%20place%20at%20a%20DHL%20warehouse%20in%20Birmingham%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20Haldenwang%2C%20the%20president%20of%20Germany's%20domestic%20intelligence%20agency%2C%20said%20in%20October%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Blucky%20coincidence%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20package%20in%20Leipzig%20caught%20fire%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20not%20during%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaldenwang%20did%20not%20explicitly%20blame%20Moscow%2C%20but%20the%20German%20news%20agency%20DPA%20reported%20that%20security%20services%20were%20worki