%20and%20very%20good%20prospects%20for%20further%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20India%20a%20great%20country%2C%20Putin%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20developing%20relations%20with%20India%20in%20all%20directions.%20India%20is%20a%20great%20country%2C%20now%20the%20largest%20in%20terms%20of%20population%3A%201.5%20billion%20people%2C%20plus%2010%20million%20every%20year.%20%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20India%20is%20leading%20the%20world%20in%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20vision%20of%20where%20and%20at%20what%20pace%20our%20relations%20will%20develop%20is%20based%20on%20today's%20realities.%20The%20volume%20of%20our%20cooperation%20is%20increasing%20many%20times%20over%2C%20every%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20was%20quoted%20by%20Russian%20news%20agency%20Tass%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20added%20that%20the%20contacts%20between%20India%20and%20Russia%20in%20the%20security%20and%20defence%20sphere%20are%20developing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20how%20many%20types%20of%20Russian%20military%20equipment%20are%20in%20service%20with%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces.%20There%20is%20a%20great%20degree%20of%20trust%20in%20this%20relationship.%20We%20don't%20just%20sell%20our%20weapons%20to%20India%3B%20we%20design%20them%20jointly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20named%20the%20BrahMos%20cruise%20missile%20project%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20we%20made%20it%20%5Bthe%20missile%5D%20fit%20for%20use%20in%20three%20environments%20-%20in%20air%2C%20in%20sea%20and%20on%20land.%20These%20projects%2C%20conducted%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20India's%20security%2C%20are%20ongoing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20widely%20known%20and%20no%20one%20has%20issues%20with%20that%2C%20but%20these%20projects%20demonstrate%20a%20high%20level%20of%20mutual%20trust%20and%20cooperation.%20So%20this%20what%20we%20will%20keep%20doing%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20and%2C%20I%20hope%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20in%20the%20more%20distant%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPutin%20acknowledged%20certain%20difficulties%20on%20the%20border%20between%20India%20and%20China%2C%20the%20agency%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20said%20wise%20and%20competent%20people%20who%20keep%20the%20future%20of%20their%20nations%20in%20mind%2C%20are%20searching%20for%20compromises%20and%20will%20eventually%20find%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20this%20approach%20continues%20to%20gain%20momentum%2C%20compromises%20can%20be%20found%2C%20and%20they%20will%20be%20found%2C%26quot%3B%20Putin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20China%20nosedived%20following%20a%20fierce%20clash%20in%20the%20Galwan%20Valley%20in%20June%202020%20that%20marked%20the%20most%20serious%20military%20conflict%20between%20the%20two%20sides%20in%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20Vikram%20Misri%20said%20in%20New%20Delhi%20that%20an%20agreement%20had%20been%20finalised%20between%20India%20and%20China%20following%20negotiations%20over%20the%20past%20several%20weeks%20and%20that%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20resolution%20of%20the%20issues%20that%20arose%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20was%20firmed%20up%20on%20patrolling%20and%20disengagement%20of%20troops%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20a%20breakthrough%20to%20end%20the%20over%20four-year%20standoff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731057120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fscbinsc8_pm-modi-vladimir-putin_625x300_09_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussian-president-vladimir-putin-say