20guys%20were%20brilliant%2C%20it%20was%20just%20one%20of%20those%20accidents%2C%26quot%3B%20Botham%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20all%20very%20quick%20and%20I'm%20OK%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFishing%20has%20been%20a%20known%20hobby%20of%20Botham's%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBotham%20and%20Merv%20Hughes%20were%20regarded%20as%20fierce%20rivals%20during%20their%20cricket%20career%2C%20particularly%20during%20Ashes%20series%20between%20England%20and%20Australia.%20Botham%20had%20also%20once%20slammed%20Hughes%20for%2022%20runs%20in%20a%20single%20over%2C%20which%20was%20then%20the%20record%20for%20the%20highest-scoring%20over%20in%20an%20Ashes%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20retirement%2C%20it%20appears%20the%20duo%20have%20put%20their%20rivalry%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731056460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frf0gjuio_ian-botham-fishing_625x300_08_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fengland-icon-ian-botham-falls-in-river-when-fishing-rescued-from-crocodiles-and-bull-sharks-report-6971852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Botham%2C%2068%2C%20was%20left%20with%20big%20bruises%20and%20scars%20on%20his%20body%20due%20to%20the%20incident.%20His%20flip-flops%20had%20reportedly%20tangled%20on%20a%20rope%20while%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20board%20the%20boat%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20accident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fengland-icon-ian-botham-falls-in-river-when-fishing-rescued-from-crocodiles-and-bull-sharks-report-6971852%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222024%20Maruti%20Suzuki%20Dzire%20Bags%205-Star%20GNCAP%20Rating%2C%20Delivers%2025.71%20Kmpl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Maruti%20Suzuki%20Dzire%20is%20the%20best-selling%20compact%20sedan%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20saloon%20has%20been%20on%20sale%20in%2