20recent%20elections%20for%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Assembly%2C%20Mr%20Vijayan%20claimed%20that%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20planned%20to%20contest%20three%20or%20four%20seats%20there%2C%20ultimately%20focusing%20on%20the%20seat%20where%20CPI(M)%20leader%20Mohammad%20Yousuf%20Tarigami%20was%20standing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20was%20to%20defeat%20Tarigami%2C%20and%20the%20BJP%20shared%20this%20objective.%20However%2C%20despite%20this%20alliance%20of%20extremists%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20people%20chose%20Tarigami%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CPI(M)%20veteran%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20in%20Wayanad%20claims%20they%20are%20different%20from%20the%20Jamaat-e-Islami%20in%20Kashmir.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20ideology%20remains%20the%20same--one%20that%20does%20not%20accept%20any%20form%20of%20democratic%20governance.%20This%20time%2C%20they%20feel%20like%20supporting%20the%20Congress-led%20UDF%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Congress%2C%20Mr%20Vijayan%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BShouldn't%20those%20who%20stand%20for%20secularism%20oppose%20all%20forms%20of%20sectarianism%3F%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BCan%20the%20Congress%20do%20that%3F%20The%20Congress%20and%20allies%2C%20including%20the%20Muslim%20League%2C%20seem%20to%20be%20making%20certain%20'sacrifices'%20to%20maintain%20their%20alliance%20with%20Jamaat-e-Islami.%20Can%20the%20Congress%20reject%20Jamaat-e-Islami's%20votes%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPI(M)%20Politburo%20member%20urged%20Congress%20leaders%20to%20recall%20a%20statement%20by%20the%20late%20Marxist%20leader%20EMS%20Namboodiripad%2C%20highlighting%20his%20firm%20stance%20against%20communal%20alliances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20in%20a%20by-election%20in%20Thalassery%2C%20EMS%20had%20openly%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20want%20RSS%20votes.%26quot%3B%20Referring%20to%20this%20example%2C%20Mr%20Vijayan%20questioned%20whether%20Congress%20co