-news%2Findian-shares-set-to-open-higher-after-fed-rate-cut-6969677%5C%22%3EIndian%20Shares%20Set%20To%20Open%20Higher%20After%20Fed%20Rate%20Cut%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrent%20crude%2C%20the%20global%20oil%20benchmark%2C%20fell%200.65%20per%20cent%20to%20USD%2075.14%20per%20barrel%20in%20futures%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20this%20dynamic%20environment%2C%20volatility%20in%20the%20USD%2FINR%20pair%20is%20expected%2C%20with%20the%20RBI%20likely%20maintaining%20a%20range%20between%2083.80%20and%2084.50.%20If%20the%20dollar's%20momentum%20stalls%20amid%20future%20Fed%20rate%20cuts%20and%20weakening%20investor%20confidence%2C%20the%20rupee%20could%20gradually%20strengthen%20toward%20the%20lower%20end%20of%20this%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pabari%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20domestic%20equity%20market%20front%2C%20Sensex%20declined%2014.23%20points%2C%20or%200.02%20per%20cent%2C%20to%2079%2C527.56%20points.%20The%20Nifty%20fell%2015.45%20points%2C%20or%200.06%20per%20cent%2C%20to%2024%2C183.90%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Institutional%20Investors%20(FIIs)%20were%20net%20sellers%20in%20the%20capital%20markets%20on%20Thursday%2C%20as%20they%20offloaded%20shares%20worth%20Rs%204%2C888.77%20crore%2C%20according%20to%20exchange%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731052140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F41trao0g_rupee-vs-usd-istock_625x300_04_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frupee-falls-to-all-time-low-of-84-37-against-us-dollar-6971447%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20rupee%20fell%205%20paise%20to%20an%20all-time%20low%20of%2084.37%20against%20the%20US%20dollar%20in%20early%20trade%20on%20Friday%2C%20weighed%20down%20by%20persistent%20foreign%20fund%20outflows%20and%20a%20muted%20trend%20in%20domestic%20equities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frupee-falls-to-all-time-low-of-84-37-against-us-dollar-6971447%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20%26quot%3BBatoge%20Toh%20Katoge%26quot%3B%20Slogan%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20Rejoinder%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20speaking%20exclusively%20with%20NDTV%2C%20called%20for%20collective%20efforts%20to%20drive%20progress%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20India.%20Assembly%20elections%20are%20scheduled%20in%20Maharashtra%20on%20November%2020%2C%20with%20Mr%20Pawar%20contesting%20against%20his%20nephew%20Yugendra%20Pawar%2C%20the%20candidate%20of%20the%20rival%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20faction%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath's%20slogan%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EBatoge%20toh%20katoge%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%20(If%20we%20divide%2C%20we%20will%20be%20cut)%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20castes%20should%20unite%20and%20think%20about%20India.%20They%20should%20think%20about%20Maharashtra.%20Development%20cannot%20happen%20by%20creating%20such%20differences%20among%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20claimed%20the%20BJP%20follows%20an%20%26quot%3B80-20%26quot%3B%20voter%20strategy%20-%20that%20seeks%20the%20support%20of%20the%2080%20per%20cent%20and%20not%20the%2020%20per%20cent%20-%20and%20this%20has%2C%20at%20times%2C%20marginalised%20minority%20voices.%20Calling%20for%20a%20return%20to%20Maharashtra's%20philosophy%20of%20inclusion%20inspired%20by%20leaders%20like%20Shivaji%2C%20Shahu%2C%20Phule%2C%20and%20Ambedkar%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20follow%20a%20political%20ideology%20in%20which%20everyone%20is%20united%20whether%20Hindu%2C%20Muslim%2C%20Dali