struggling%20to%20support%20them%20as%20not%20all%20of%20it%20is%20prime%20habitat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%20conservationists%20have%20also%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20creating%20safe%20forest%20corridors%20so%20the%20tigers%20of%20Ranthambore%20can%20safely%20disperse%20to%20other%20forests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20also%20been%20instances%20of%20villagers%20poisoning%20tigers%20in%20the%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20tiger%20was%20stoned%20and%20axed%20to%20death%2C%20allegedly%20by%20villagers%20who%20were%20angry%20over%20a%20goatherd%20being%20killed%20in%20a%20tiger%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731046440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F0hb268n8_ranthambore-tigers_625x300_08_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franthambore-national-park-tigers-traced-official-as-report-flags-25-missing-tigers-6970227%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajasthan's%20Chief%20Wildlife%20Warden%20said%20this%20week%20that%2025%20tigers%20in%20Ranthambore%20National%20Park%20have%20gone%20missing%20over%20the%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Franthambore-national-park-tigers-traced-official-as-report-flags-25-missing-tigers-6970227%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22COP29%20chief%20exec%20filmed%20promoting%20fossil%20fuel%20deals%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731045988000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fdf3b%2Flive%2F6dc02100-9da4-11ef-8538-e1655f5a8342.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcrmzvdn9e18o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Undercover%20filming%20shows%20COP29%20chief%20exec%20discussing%20new%20oil%20and%20gas%20projects%20ahead%20of%20climate%20summit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A295%2C