20slowly%20through%20Asia.%20I%20started%20my%20travels%20in%20India%2C%20where%20I%20spent%2010%20days%20at%20a%20silent%20meditation%20retreat%2C%20attended%20teachings%20by%20the%20Dalai%20Lama%2C%20and%20took%20a%20yoga%20teacher%20training.%20I%20promptly%20got%20hooked%20on%20teaching%20yoga.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20months%20in%20India%2C%20I%20continued%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-pack-traveling-in-southeast-asia-singapore-thailand-bali-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaking%20my%20way%20through%20Asia%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20eight%20more%20months.%20I%20swam%20in%20the%20crystal%20clear%20waters%20of%20the%20Maldives%2C%20visited%20healers%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-family-kids-bali-decompress-relocate-slow-life-work-remote-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20witnessed%20breathtaking%20sunrise%20views%20from%20mountaintops%20in%20Laos%2C%20went%20island-hopping%20through%20the%20Philippines%2C%20rode%20motorbikes%20around%20Thailand's%20islands%2C%20and%20discovered%20ancient%20pagodas%20in%20Myanmar%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20living%20in%20much%20of%20Asia%20is%20so%20low%20that%20savings%20can%20stretch%20a%20long%20way.%20I%20have%20high%20standards%20for%20my%20accommodations%2C%20and%20while%20traveling%2C%20I%20usually%20spent%20around%20%2420%20to%20%2425%20per%20night%20on%20hotels.%20Lower-maintenance%20friends%20of%20mine%20found%20simpler%20places%20for%20%246%20per%20night%20in%20India.%20Meals%20usually%20cost%20around%20%243.%20After%20six%20weeks%20in%20India%2C%20I%20considered%20a%20lunch%20bill%20of%20%245%20to%20be%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab294bd6-6046-4d9c-bc51-86c39da588b2%5C%22%3EThere%20have%20been%20times%20along%20the%20way%20when%20I've%20felt%20lost%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20time%20to%20time%2C%20I%20experienced%20stretches%20of%20feeling%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A