news-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fprince-william-heckled-as-he-finishes-cape-town-tour-but-protestors-dwarfed-by-crowds-13249990%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fprince-william-heckled-as-he-finishes-cape-town-tour-but-protestors-dwarfed-by-crowds-13249990%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Beyond%20Numbers%3A%20How%20Flexible%20Funding%20Fuels%20Lasting%20Impact%20in%20Women-Led%20Indian%20NGOs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOnly%2025%20to%2030%20percent%20of%20NGOs%20in%20India%20are%20led%20by%20women%20despite%20women%20comprising%2045%20percent%20of%20the%20staff%20in%20these%20NGOs.%20What%20are%20their%20everyday%20struggles%20and%20how%20are%20they%20breaking%20barriers%20and%20building%20new%20pathways%20out%20of%20this%20inequity%3F%20Can%20investing%20in%20women-led%20organisations%20rebuild%20a%20more%20equitable%20India%20for%20women%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20the%20stories%20and%20experiences%20of%20M%20Jayam%2C%20Neelam%20Besra%2C%20Shabina%2C%20Pushpa%20and%20many%20others%2C%20we%20explore%20the%20possibilities%20of%20gender-expansive%20and%20lasting%20impact%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20the%20odds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBreaking%20the%20shackles%20of%20bonded%20labour%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJayam%20%3Cem%3EAkka%20%3C%2Fem%3E(%E2%80%98elder%20sister%E2%80%99%20in%20Tamil%2C%20a%20term%20affectionately%20used%20by%20her%20team%20and%20community)%20was%20born%20into%20a%20family%20bound%20by%20bonded%20labour.%20She%20occasionally%20speaks%20courageously%20about%20the%20indignities%20of%20her%20early%20years%2C%20recalling%20tasks%20assigned%20to%20Dalit%20women%20and%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20including%20washing%20menstrual%20clothes%20for%20influential%20households%20where%20her%20father%20served%20as%20a%20bonded%20labourer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnwilling%20to%20continue%20a%20life%20of%20indignity%20and%20determined%20to%20break%20this%20cycle%20of%20intergenerational%20exploitation%2C%20she%20founded%20Salem%20People%20Trust%20(SPT).%20Since%202007%2C%20SPT%20has%20rescued%20and%20rehabilitated%20376%20bonded%20labourers%2C%20helped%201%2C372%20children%20return%20to%20school%20free%20from%20bonded%20labour%2C%20and%20continues%20to%20advocate%20for%20child%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20our%20initial%20focus%20was%20on%20ending%20bonded%20labour%2C%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20freed%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20those%20affected%2C%20with%20their%20children%20now%20attending%20school.%20Our%20board%20members%20and%20staff%20are%20chosen%20from%20former%20bonded%20labourers%20and%20others%20with%20lived%20experiences%2C%20including%20child%20labour%20and%20the%20pressures%20of%20sex-selective%20abortion.%20We%20believe%20those%20who%20have%20lived%20through%20these%20challenges%20are%20best%20positioned%20to%20serve%20as%20community%20organisers%20and%20leaders.%20Their%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20struggles%20allows%20us%20to%20effectively%20address%20the%20needs%20and%20bring%20meaningful%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20women%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20with%20flexible%20funding%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20often%20overlook%20that%20NGOs%20and%20their%20leaders%20need%20support%20to%20sustain%20their%20invaluable%20work.%20Office%20infrastructure%2C%20staff%20medical%20insurance%2C%20well-being%2C%20and%20capacity-building%20all%20demand%20investment%20beyond%20traditional%20community%20programmes%20to%20empower%20them%20to%20continue%20their%20efforts%20sustainably%20and%20without%20fear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20flexible%20funding%20enables%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20with%20flexible%20support%20from%20the%20Rebuild%20India%20Fund%2C%20Jayam%20%3Cem%3EAkka%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20supporting%2010%20fellows%20to%20teach%20in%20five%20schools%20an