ed%20this%20with%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20nephrologist%2C%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%2C%20they%20knew%20that%20they%20had%20to%20address%20this%20gap.%20Another%20friend%20of%20Prabhat%E2%80%99s%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%2C%20a%20Chartered%20Accountant%2C%20joined%20them%20in%20their%20mission%20to%20make%20quality%20dialysis%20care%20accessible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20government%20report%2C%20over%202.2%20lakh%20patients%20are%20diagnosed%20with%20end-stage%20renal%20disease%20(ESRD)%20every%20year%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20demand%20of%203.4%20crore%20dialysis%20sessions%20annually.%20The%20challenge%20lies%20in%20the%20insufficient%20number%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20across%20the%20country.%20Prabhat%20states%20that%20while%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20at%20least%2015%2C000%20dialysis%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%20only%205%2C000%20exist%2C%20highlighting%20a%20critical%20need%20for%20more%20facilities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%20July%202017%2C%20VitusCare%20Medlife%20Pvt.%20Ltd%20aims%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20Tier%202%20and%203%20towns.%20Over%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20they%20have%20established%2035%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20seven%20states%20across%20North%20India%2C%20providing%20over%2015%2C000%20sessions%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20idea%20was%20very%20clear%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20vision%20comes%20to%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20really%20united%20the%20three%20founders%20was%20their%20shared%20background%20from%20Tier%202%20cities.%20Prabhat%2C%20a%20lawyer%20from%20Jabalpur.%20Dr%20Saurabh%20from%20Dehradun%20with%2018%20years%20of%20experience%2C%20and%20Pankaj%20from%20Agra%2C%20a%20corporate%20finance%20expert%2C%20all%20recognised%20the%20pressing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333216%2Fiit-guwahati-invents-sensor-for-diabetes-diet-low-glycemic-index-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneed%20for%20better%20care%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20his%20parents%20to%20Gurgaon%20in%202015%2C%20Prabhat%20started%20brainstorming%20possible%20solutions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoving%20my%20parents%20out%20of%20their%20comfort%20zone%20was%20not%20easy.%20I%20was%20shocked%20that%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20quality%20dialysis%20centres%20in%20Jabalpur%2C%20which%20is%20not%20a%20small%20city.%20I%20found%20people%20travelling%20100%20km%20daily%20for%20dialysis%2C%20and%20it%20was%20heartbreaking.%20While%20I%20could%20relocate%20my%20father%2C%20not%20everyone%20has%20that%20luxury%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Prabhat%2C%20CEO%20of%20VitusCare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvituscare-1730297932.jpeg%3Ffit%3D1600%252C739%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20VitusCare%20centre%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvituscare-1730297932.jpeg%3Fw%3D1600%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvituscare-1730297932.jpeg%3Fresize%3D300%252C139%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvituscare-1730297932.jpeg%3Fresize%3D500%252C231%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvituscare-1730297932.jpeg%3Fresize%3D768%252C355%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvituscare-1730297932.jpeg%3Fresize%3D1536%252C709%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Fvituscare-1730297932.jpeg%3Fresize%3D150%252C69%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373618%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22739%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20VitusCare%20centre%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20Lancet%20report%2C%20almost%2060%20percent%20of%20patients%20on%20dialysis%20in%20the%20country%20have%20to%20travel%20over%2050%20km%2C%20and%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20live%20over%20100%20km%20away%20from%20a%20facility.%20Prabhat%20knew%20that%20the%20solution%20to%20this%20was%20providing%20quality%20care%20in%20the%20hinterlands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20job%2C%20and%20along%20with%20the%20other%20two%20co-founders%2C%20set%20up%20the%20first%20VitusCare%20dialysis%20centre%20in%20Aligarh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20was%20very%20clear%3A%20we%20wanted%20quality%20dialysis%20therapy%20centres%20in%20cities%20which%20lack%20accessibility.%20Due%20to%20the%20distance%2C%20people%20often%20miss%20their%20dialysis%20sessions%2C%20leading%20to%20poor%20outcomes.%20In%20India%2C%20a%20CKD%20patient%20on%20dialysis%20lives%2C%20on%20average%2C%20for%20four%20years%2C%20while%20in%20the%20West%2C%20patients%20live%20for%20over%2015%20years.%20We%20need%20to%20improve%20outcomes%20for%20our%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20emphasises%20Prabhat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChronic%20kidney%20disease%20(CKD)%20affects%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20although%20the%20exact%20number%20of%20patients%20remains%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Founders%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%20and%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%20(L-R)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D300%252C157%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D500%252C262%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D768%252C402%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-2024-10-30T195140.909-1730298116.jpg%3Fresize%3D150%252C79%26amp%3Bquality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-373632%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFounders%20Prabhat%20Shrivastava%2C%20Pankaj%20Tandon%20and%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal%20(L-R)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDialysis%20is%20a%20vital%20treatment%20for%20patients%20with%20kidney%20failure%2C%20filtering%20waste%20products%20and%20excess%20fluid%20from%20the%20blood%20when%20the%20kidneys%20can%20no%20longer%20function%20properly.%20This%20life-saving%20procedure%20involves%20removing%20blood%20from%20the%20body%20through%20a%20needle%2C%20passing%20it%20through%20a%20machine%20to%20filter%20out%20harmful%20substances%2C%20and%20then%20returning%20the%20clean%20blood%20to%20the%20body.%20Typically%2C%20dialysis%20becomes%20necessary%20when%20kidney%20function%20declines%20significantly%2C%20reaching%20a%20point%20where%20natural%20filtration%20is%20insufficient%20to%20support%20the%20body%E2%80%99s%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Saurabh%20Pokhariyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20problem%20of%20accessibility%20remains%2C%20the%20other%20concern%20is%20affordability.%20To%20provide%20dialysis%20at%20no%20cost%2C%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20National%20Dialysis%20Programme%20(PMNDP)%20was%20rolled%20out%20in%20April%202016.%20The%20programme%20has%20two%20components%3A%20Hemodialysis%20(HD)%20services%20and%20Peritoneal%20dialysis%20(PD)%20services.%20Under%20the%20PMNDP%2C%20the%20government%20has%20set%20up%201%2C530%20centres%20across%20the%20country%2C%20still%20leaving%20a%20significant%20gap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKey%20issues%20include%20high%20treatment%20costs%2C%20limited%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F344858%2Fthe-hans-foundation-dialysis-chronic-kidney-disease-renal-care-centre-treat-underprivileged-rural-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eavailability%20of%20dialysis%20centres%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20accessibility%20barriers%20for%20patients%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20and%20a%20shortage%20of%20skilled%20healthcare%20professionals.%20Additionally%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20public%20awareness%20about%20kidney%20disease%20and%20dialysis%20options%20further%20complicates%20timely%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20Dialysis%20Convenient%3A%20How%20VitusCare%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVitusCare%20provides%20three%20forms%20of%20patient%20care%3A%20the%20in-centre%20dialysis%20model%2C%20where%20they%20set%20up%20centres%20inside%20existing%20hospitals%20in%20Tier%202%20and%203%20cities%20(95%20percent%20of%20their%20centres)%2C%20standalone%20centres%20where%20they%20open%20facilities%20in%20areas%20without%20hospitals%2C%20and%20at-home%20dialysis%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20their%20most%20popular%20form%20of%20care%2C%20the%20in-centre%20dialysis%20model%2C%20Prabhat%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20identify%20a%20space%2C%20develop%20and%20prepare%20it.%20We%20employ%20support%20staff%20in%20the%20centres.%20Using%20a%20hub-and-spoke%20model%2C%20we%20monitor%20all%20centres%20through%20our%20central%20team%20in%20Gurgaon.%20We%20have%20an%20operations%20team%20that%20monitors%20each%20centre%2C%20ensuring%20quality%20through%20strict%20SOPs.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22