0in%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eabout%20dyslexia.%20It%20was%20literally%20describing%20me.%20I%20did%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20maths%20and%20English%2C%20the%20reversing%20%5Bof%20the%20letters%5D%20%E2%80%98B%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98D%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20confusion%20between%20left%20and%20right%20%5Bdirections%5D.%20After%20reading%20the%20article%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20get%20me%20tested%20%5Bfor%20dyslexia%5D.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20there%20was%20hardly%20any%20awareness.%20%5BBut%5D%20At%20least%20now%2C%20my%20struggle%20had%20a%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Pradeep%2C%20dyslexia%20brings%20a%20lot%20of%20strength%20and%20weakness.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20this%20day%2C%20I%20do%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20reading.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20I%20can%20sit%20down%20and%20then%20read%20a%20book.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20never%20read%20a%20novel%20or%20a%20book%20to%20date%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20for%20me.%20I%20do%20make%20spelling%20mistakes%20even%20today.%20But%20I%20understand%20how%20things%20work.%20On%20a%20very%20process%20level%2C%20I%20can%20decipher%20how%20an%20engineering%20component%20would%20work.%20My%20strengths%20lie%20in%20figuring%20out%20niche%20problems%20where%20people%20are%20not%20able%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20conventionally.%20I%20can%20look%20at%20a%20problem%20and%20give%20it%20solutions%20in%20a%20way%20that%20nobody%20else%20can%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMDA-Image-1730298862.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628