%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22864%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EMDA%20has%20faithfully%20served%20children%20with%20dyslexia%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20personal%20motivation%20for%20establishing%20MDA%20was%20the%20opportunity%20to%20meet%20professionals%20who%20could%20help%20my%20son.%20Initially%2C%20the%20MDA%20encountered%20a%20lot%20of%20problems.%20Firstly%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20clarity%20about%20what%20dyslexia%20is.%20Many%20parents%20were%20in%20denial%20that%20their%20children%20could%20have%20dyslexia.%20There%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20in%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20thought%20that%20we%20were%20supporting%20%E2%80%98dumb%E2%80%99%20children.%20But%20we%20would%20overcome%20these%20challenges%20over%20time%20through%20our%20relentless%20awareness%20programmes%2C%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20parents%2C%20schools%20and%20the%20general%20public%20through%20the%20media%2C%20while%20also%20actively%20providing%20special%20assistance%20to%20dyslexic%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20does%20MDA%20do%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20MDA%20started%20with%20training%20teachers%20to%20help%20children%20with%20dyslexia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20D%20Chandrasekhar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20opened%20a%20remediation%20centre%2C%20both%20part-time%20and%20full-time%2C%20for%20children%20and%20also%20got%20a%20few%20of%20our%20special%20educators%20trained%20to%20carry%20out%20assessments.%20We