t%20levels%20of%20dyslexia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20remediation%20sessions%20for%20children%20are%20done%20through%20the%20ALRC.%20This%20includes%20an%C2%A0%20Individual%20Education%20Program%20(IEP)%2C%20which%20according%20to%20the%20MDA%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20drawn%20out%20for%20the%20child%20based%20on%20his%2Fher%20strengths%20and%20needs.%E2%80%9D%20The%20IEP%20consists%20of%20%E2%80%9Cskill%20building%2C%20need-based%20and%20activity%20oriented%20learning%E2%80%9D.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20ALRC%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98holistic%20development%20of%20the%20child%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20nurture%20their%20talents%20and%20interests%20%E2%80%94%20including%20co-curricular%20activities%20like%20yoga%2C%20music%2C%20dramatics%2C%20arts%20and%20crafts%2C%20and%20games%2C%20besides%20something%20called%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHydra%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20website%2C%20%E2%80%9CHydra%20is%20one%20of%20the%20arms%20of%20MDA%20focussed%20on%20nurturing%20the%20natural%20potential%20of%20children.%20The%20team%20at%20Hydra%20consists%20of%20trained%20teachers%20and%20mental%20health%20professionals%20and%20works%20in%20technical%20partnership%20with%20Vidya%20Sagar%20%5Ba%20Chennai-based%20non-profit%20empowering%20people%20with%20disabilities%5D.%20The%20environment%20at%20Hydra%20is%20caring%20and%20non-threatening.%20This%20encourages%20the%20children%20to%20let%20go%20of%20any%20stress%20and%20feelings%20of%20low%20self-worth%20that%20often%20accompany%20the%20condition%20of%20dyslexia.%20It%20helps%20them%20feel%20accepted%20for%20who%20they%20are.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FVNHQZmfjK0s%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMDA%20also%20engages%20in%20Occupational%20Therapy%2C%20a%20key%20component%20of%20remediation.%20This%20focuses%20%E2%80%9Con%20helping%20children%20with%20physical%20ability%2C%20sensory%20integration%2C%20attention%2C%20and%20concentration%20difficulty%20to%20enhance%20their%20skills%20along%20with%20self-esteem%20and%20performance%20in%20the%20classroom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20you%20have%20counselling%2C%20where%20the%20ALRC%20partners%20with%20qualified%20professionals%20to%20provide%20counselling%20for%20children%20and%20parents%20as%20part%20of%20the%20personality%20development%20of%20the%20child.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20an%20in-house%20counsellor%20who%20interacts%20with%20the%20child%20and%20the%20parent%20and%20also%20conducts%20periodic%20workshops%20for%20them.%20The%20teachers%20are%20also%20given%20orientation%20on%20child%20behaviour%20to%20help%20them%20handle%20different%20behavioural%20issues%20in%20the%20classroom%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20website%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EResults%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20misconceptions%20that%20people%20have%20about%20dyslexic%20children%20is%20that%20they%20are%20not%20intelligent.%20Actually%2C%20they%20are%20very%20intelligent%20with%20an%20IQ%20of%20more%20than%2085.%20It%20is%20very%20easy%20to%20work%20with%20them%20once%20we%20take%20the%20right%20approach.%20MDA%20has%20removed%20the%20misconceptions%20by%20demonstrating%20the%20remedial%20programmes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20three%20decades%2C%20Chandrasekhar%20claims%20that%20MDA%20has%20directly%20assisted%20more%20than%201%2C500%20children%20in%20their%20full-time%20remediation%20centre%2C%20and%20provided%20part-time%20remediation%20for%203%2C000%20children.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20trained%20more%20than%202%2C000%20teachers%20and%20conducted%20training%20programmes%20in%20over%20400%20schools.%20We%20have%20also%20set%20up%20resource%20rooms%20for%20dyslexic%20children%20in%20nearly%20200%20schools%20that%20benefit%2010%2C000%20of%20them%20year%20on%20year%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Chandrasekhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20far%20has%20our%20education%20system%20come%20in%20assisting%20children%20with%20dyslexia%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20education%20system%20has%20shown%20a%20lot%20of%20understanding%20towards%20the%20needs%20of%20dyslexic%20children.%20A%20lot%20of%20concessions%20are%20offered%20during%20public%20exams.%20Dyslexic%20children%20are%20eligible%20for%20all%20the%20benefits%20under%20the%20Disabilities%20Act.%20Yet%2C%20we%20have%20a%20long%20way%20to%20go.%20Awareness%20in%20schools%20is%20still%20very%20low%2C%20especially%20among%20teachers.%20While%20private%20schools%20easily%20understand%20the%20problems%20associated%20with%20dyslexia%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20still%20not%20a%20priority%20in%20government%20schools.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20D%20Chandrasekhar)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1730518200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FMDA-Image-2-1730298658.jpg%3Fw%3D1200%26quality%3D89%26amp%3Bssl%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D373627%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%201992%2C%20a%20compassionate%20group%20of%20parents%2C%20educators%2C%20and%20philanthropists%20came%20together%20to%20create%20the%20Madras%20Dyslexia%20Association%20(MDA).%20Their%20mission%20is%20to%20support%20children%20with%20dyslexia%20through%20pragmatic%20solutions%2C%20focusing%20on%20personalized%20education%20and%20creating%20an%20understanding%20environment%20that%20empowers%20these%20children%20to%20thrive%20academically%20and%20socially.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F373627%2Fhelping-dyslexic-children-with-learning-education-madras-dyslexia-association-iit-madras%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Aashraya%20on%20the%20Ganga%E2%80%99%3A%20This%20Dad%20Built%20a%20Sustainable%20Homestay%20for%20His%20Daughters%20in%20Rishikesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMaybe%20what%20I%20really%20want%20is%20to%20be%20near%20the%20river.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDepi%20Chaudhry%20(56)%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20an%20inkling%20that%20this%20whim%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20would%20someday%20transform%20into%20his%20dream%2C%20%E2%80%98Aashraya%20on%20the%20Ganga%E2%80%99.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358205%2Ftiny-farm-fort-homestay-rishikesh-raghav-ansh-kumar-delhi-architects-cob-sustainable-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20homestay%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20alienated%20from%20the%20cacophony%20of%20Rishikesh%2C%20and%20the%20AQI%20(Air%20Quality%20Index)%20here%20is%20an%20outlier%2C%20standing%20at%2016%20as%20of%2024%20October%202024%2C%20in%20stark%20contrast%20to%20North%20India%E2%80%99s%20statistics%2C%20which%20border%20on%20200.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Depi%2C%20a%20multi-hyphenate%20%E2%80%94-%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20an%20avid%20trekker%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20a%20homestay%20owner%20and%20a%20father%20to%20three%20girls%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20the%20homestay%20was%20a%20corollary%20of%20the%20sustainable%20life%20he%20envisioned%20for%20his%20daughters%20as%20they%20got%20older.%20%E2%80%9CI%20thought%20this%20%5Bthe%20cottages%5D%20would%20encourage%20them%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20outdoors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetting%20us%20in%20on%20why%20he%20was%20keen%20to%20live%20near%20the%20River%20Ganges%2C%20he%20recalls%20one%20of%20his%20many%20trekking%20expeditions.%20After%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20move%20from%20Bengaluru%20to%20Gurugram%20in%202002%2C%20Depi%20was%20busy%20finding%20his%20rhythm%20as%20a%20stay-at-home%20dad.%20His%20day%2C%20which%20began%20with%20neatly%20arranging%20three%20tiffin%20boxes%20%E2%80%94%20guessing%20which%20snacks%20would%20thrill%20his%20little%20girls%20%E2%80%94%20often%20ended%20with%20him%20preparing%20lavish%20dinners%20following%20homework%20sessions%20in%20the%20evenings.%20Naturally%2C%20when%20his%20daughters%20moved%20to%20boarding%20school%20in%20later%20years%2C%20the%20empty%20nest%20brought%20an%20ache%20for%20company%2C%20which%20Depi%20found%20in%20nature.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201000px)%20100vw%2C%201000px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2FAashraya-on-the-Ganga-1_11zon-1730287955.jpg%3Ffit%3D1200%252C628%26quality%3D89%26ssl%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aashraya%20on%20the%20Ganga%20is%20a%20dream%20of%20Depi%20Chaudhry%20who%20built%20three%20cottages%2C%20one%20each%20for%20his%20daughters%2C%20and%20has%20now%20turned%20the%20property%20into%20a%20homestay%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fen-media.thebetterindia